<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>第18章 同時実行制御 - 目次</title>
    <style>
        /* 基本スタイル設定 */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Hiragino Sans', 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
        }
        
        /* スライドコンテナ - 4:3比率を厳密に */
        .slide {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            padding: 60px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            margin: 0 auto;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        /* ヘッダー */
        .slide-header {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e3a5f;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #4a7ba7;
        }
        
        /* フッター */
        .slide-footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 60px;
            right: 60px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .slide-number {
            font-weight: bold;
            background: #1e3a5f;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }
        
        /* 目次コンテンツ */
        .toc-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .toc-column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 25px;
        }
        
        .toc-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .toc-number {
            background: #4a7ba7;
            color: white;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .toc-content {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .toc-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e3a5f;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .toc-subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        /* 印刷用設定 */
        @media print {
            body {
                margin: 0;
                background: white;
            }
            
            .slide {
                width: 100vw;
                height: 100vh;
                box-shadow: none;
                page-break-after: always;
            }
        }
        
        @page {
            size: landscape;
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- スライド2: 目次 -->
    <div class="slide">
        <h2 class="slide-header">目次</h2>
        
        <div class="toc-container">
            <div class="toc-column">
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <div class="toc-number">1</div>
                    <div class="toc-content">
                        <div class="toc-title">イントロダクション</div>
                        <div class="toc-subtitle">同時実行制御の必要性と問題例</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <div class="toc-number">2</div>
                    <div class="toc-content">
                        <div class="toc-title">ロックベースプロトコル</div>
                        <div class="toc-subtitle">共有・排他ロックと互換性</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <div class="toc-number">3</div>
                    <div class="toc-content">
                        <div class="toc-title">2相ロックプロトコル</div>
                        <div class="toc-subtitle">成長・収縮フェーズと変種</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <div class="toc-number">4</div>
                    <div class="toc-content">
                        <div class="toc-title">グラフベースプロトコル</div>
                        <div class="toc-subtitle">ツリープロトコルとその特性</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="toc-column">
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <div class="toc-number">5</div>
                    <div class="toc-content">
                        <div class="toc-title">デッドロック処理</div>
                        <div class="toc-subtitle">防止・検出・回復手法</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <div class="toc-number">6</div>
                    <div class="toc-content">
                        <div class="toc-title">複数粒度ロック</div>
                        <div class="toc-subtitle">階層構造と意図ロック</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <div class="toc-number">7</div>
                    <div class="toc-content">
                        <div class="toc-title">高度なトピック</div>
                        <div class="toc-subtitle">ファントム現象・タイムスタンプ・スナップショット分離</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <div class="toc-number">8</div>
                    <div class="toc-content">
                        <div class="toc-title">実用的考慮事項</div>
                        <div class="toc-subtitle">商用システムでの実装</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="slide-footer">
            <div></div>
            <div class="slide-number">2</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>